OL,3,CParents fear proposed SEND reforms
OL,4,Ccould impact vital support
OL,6,FFamilies have staged a protest against
OL,7,Fplanned government reforms to special
OL,8,Feducational needs and disabilities
OL,9,F(SEND) support for children.
OL,11,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,12,Fthe current system "does not work" for
OL,13,Fchildren and parents, with Education
OL,14,FSecretary Ms Phillipson saying too
OL,15,Fmany parents are having to "fight" for
OL,16,Fthe right support for their child.
OL,18,FBut parents say new plans to change
OL,19,Fthe system could strip many children
OL,20,Fof the crucial support they rely on.
OL,26,@tD@TOUtD@bO]wD@\OUwD@bO]
