OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778609471
OL,3,CParents fear proposed SEND reforms
OL,4,Ccould impact vital support
OL,6,FFamilies gathered in Liverpool on
OL,7,FSaturday to voice concerns that the
OL,8,Fproposed changes to the SEND system
OL,9,Fwill make it harder for children to
OL,10,Faccess Education Health and Care Plans
OL,11,F(EHCPs), which currently guarantee
OL,12,Fextra help in school.
OL,14,FMandy Smith from the SEND National
OL,15,FCrisis Campaign explained: "The
OL,16,Fgovernment are proposing that only the
OL,17,Fmost complex children have an
OL,18,Feducation health and care plan, EHCP.
OL,26,@wD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778609471
OL,3,CParents fear proposed SEND reforms
OL,4,Ccould impact vital support
OL,6,F"Without that support, a lot of
OL,7,Fchildren are not going to be able to
OL,8,Fattend school; they might be out of
OL,9,Fschool."
OL,11,FParents fear that children who
OL,12,Fcurrently have EHCPs may lose them
OL,13,Funder the new system.
OL,15,FSpending on support for children with
OL,16,Fspecial educational needs and
OL,17,Fdisabilities (SEND) has ballooned in
OL,18,Frecent years amid rising demand,
OL,19,Fleading to spiralling costs for
OL,20,Fcouncils and large deficits.
OL,26,@qD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
