PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778609471
OL,3,CParents fear proposed SEND reforms
OL,4,Ccould impact vital support
OL,6,FUnder the new plans, 11-year-old Alfie
OL,7,FRimmer, who currently receives
OL,8,Fsupport, could lose his place at a
OL,9,Fspecial independent school.
OL,11,FAlfie said "I don't know what it'll be
OL,12,Flike if I weren't in the independent
OL,13,Fschool because my education will fall
OL,14,Fdown a lot."
OL,16,FHis mum, Ashlea Rimmer, added: "I have
OL,17,Fbeen fighting this system for six
OL,18,Fyears now with my son Alfie, and it's
OL,19,Fexhausting.
OL,26,@xD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
