OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778609471
OL,3,CParents fear proposed SEND reforms
OL,4,Ccould impact vital support
OL,6,F"A lot of families are in the same
OL,7,Fboat, they are fighting for EHCPs, for
OL,8,Feducation, psychiatrists, occupational
OL,9,Ftherapy, speech and language. It
OL,10,Fshouldn't have to be a fight to get
OL,11,Fwhat your child needs."
OL,13,FIn England, if a child needs more
OL,14,Fsupport than is typically provided in
OL,15,Fmainstream schools, their parent or
OL,16,Fcarer can apply for an education,
OL,17,Fhealth and care plan (EHCP), which
OL,18,Fsets out the extra support they are
OL,19,Fentitled to.
OL,26,@sD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
